Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.44,0:00:20.28,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}脚下的街道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.28,0:00:22.86,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8\fad(0,521)}今天也一如往常
