Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.21,0:00:34.42,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}弄脏的衬衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.42,0:00:36.38,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}沾染上了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:40.34,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}这自欺欺人的谎言…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.34,0:00:45.47,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8\fad(0,348)}我到底在保护什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:49.89,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}不畏失去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.89,0:00:53.60,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}即便长大成人 也心怀梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.60,0:00:55.61,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}因为我只希望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:58.11,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}自己能将这些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.11,0:01:01.03,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8\fad(0,351)}视为骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:05.07,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}吐出来 舍弃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.07,0:01:06.95,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.95,0:01:08.70,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8\fad(0,347)}回忆起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:10.62,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}这样就好
