Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.99,0:22:31.70,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}误入这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:34.24,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(0,349)}在此相遇的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.62,0:22:39.58,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(0,1058)}最后一次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.38,0:22:53.85,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}东奔西走 苦苦找寻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.22,0:22:57.43,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(0,349)}却毫无头绪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.02,0:23:03.48,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}狂风巨浪 风起云涌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:07.07,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(0,355)}这残酷世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:10.95,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}你用最强的光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.95,0:23:13.12,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}照亮我模糊而单调的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.45,0:23:15.20,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}「谢谢你」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.54,0:23:17.58,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(0,354)}我不是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.16,0:23:20.46,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}在昏沉的阴天下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.46,0:23:23.00,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}Cry Cry哭也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:27.13,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(0,353)}抓住云间那一缕光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.76,0:23:30.05,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}这鲜红的证明流淌着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.05,0:23:32.43,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}疼痛难忍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:37.06,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}最后一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.18,0:23:39.56,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(525,0)}希望永不分离
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.56,0:23:42.06,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}希望笑容永驻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.06,0:23:46.19,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}希望生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.19,0:23:49.24,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}Ah 在这湛蓝的晴空下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.24,0:23:55.24,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(0,518)}许下一个心愿
